'''Ibragim Yuryevich Tsallagov''' ({{lang-ru|Ибрагим Юрьевич Цаллагов}}; born 12 December 1990) is a [[Russia]]n professional [[Association football|football]] player. He plays for [[FC Rubin Kazan|Rubin Kazan]] on loan from [[FC Zenit Saint Petersburg|Zenit St. Petersburg]]. He primarily plays as [[right back]] and occasionally as [[defensive midfielder]].
==Club career==
He made his [[Russian Premier League]] debut on 13 March 2010 for [[FC Krylia Sovetov Samara]] in a game against [[FC Zenit Saint Petersburg|FC Zenit St. Petersburg]].<ref>[http://www.rfpl.org/reports/id6554 Game report by Russian Premier League] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111113052809/http://www.rfpl.org/reports/id6554 |date=November 13, 2011 }}</ref>
On 30 December 2016, he signed a 3.5-year contract with [[FC Zenit Saint Petersburg]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[FC Zenit Saint Petersburg]]|url=http://fc-zenit.ru/news/feed/2016/12/30/ibragim-tsallagov-prisoedinilsya-k-zenitu/|script-title=ru:Ибрагим Цаллагов присоединился к «Зениту»|date=30 December 2016|language=Russian}}</ref>
On 2 August 2017, he joined [[FC Dynamo Moscow]] on loan for the 2017–18 season.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[FC Dynamo Moscow]]|url=http://fcdynamo.ru/news/events/?id_4=12954|script-title=ru:Цаллагов – в «Динамо»!|date=2 August 2017|language=Russian}}</ref> On 28 July 2018, he moved on loan to [[FC Rubin Kazan]] for the 2018–19 season.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[FC Rubin Kazan]]|url=http://rubin-kazan.ru/ru/news_items/8002|title=Ибрагим Цаллагов - в «Рубине» на правах аренды|date=27 July 2018|language=Russian}}</ref>
