'''Isa Abduldzhalilovich Baytiyev''' ({{lang-ru|Иса Абдулжалилович Байтиев}}; born 2 December 1966) is a [[Russia]]n professional [[Association football|football]] coach and a former player.
He currently is an assistant manager of [[FC Terek Grozny]] in the [[Russian Premier League]].
