==Biography==
Juncai is from [[Shanxi]] Province, [[China]]. He was verified as China's tallest man on 23 November 2010 at {{convert|2.42|m|sp=us}}. Zhang went to the hospital in April 2009, to visit his friend, the {{convert|2.34|m|sp=us|adj=on}} tallest living woman [[Yao Defen]]. 

